			<h4 class="special-offer-subheader">
				What's better than craft beers curated to your taste preferences and delivered to your door? 
				Being able to buy <span>more</span> of those beers, of course!
			</h4>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="row">
		<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4">
